# Android related
#
# NOTE (Release Audit, RC-1.0.0): as of v1.0.0, android/ is a real,
# committed platform folder (previously missing entirely — see
# docs/release/KNOWN_ISSUES.md item 1) rather than something
# regenerated fresh by CI on every run. gradlew / gradlew.bat are
# therefore intentionally NOT ignored below (unlike Flutter's
# default template) so every checkout has a working, reproducible
# build without needing `flutter create` to run first.
# gradle-wrapper.jar remains ignored: it's a binary Flutter's own
# tooling supplies/refreshes at build time from its bundled
# template, so it doesn't need to be (and conventionally isn't)
# committed by hand.
**/android/**/gradle-wrapper.jar
**/android/.gradle
**/android/captures/
**/android/local.properties
**/android/**/GeneratedPluginRegistrant.java
**/android/key.properties
*.jks

# Symbolication related
app.*.symbols

# Obfuscation related
app.*.map.json

# Exceptions to above rules.
!/packages/flutter_tools/test/data/dart_dependencies_test/**/.packages
